<p>英 /hɔːs/    美 /hɔːrs/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>马：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ride a horse
骑马</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>get off / on a horse
下/上马</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>eat like a horse
吃得很多</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="hold-your-horses">hold your horses</h3>
<p>1.<strong>慢点；别急</strong>  </p></div>